<div class="wp-block-cover" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:0;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-bottom:0;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:494px;aspect-ratio:unset;aspect-ratio:unset;"><img width="2000" height="730" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-23276 size-full" alt="A tattooed person suspends from hooks, laying flat, one leg higher than the other. Their head is back, and they seem to be smiling, dark hair dangling like an anime character." src="https://www-img.bme.com/uploads/2025/04/005022650018.jpg" style="object-position:77% 51%" data-object-fit="cover" data-object-position="77% 51%" srcset="https://www-img.bme.com/uploads/2025/04/005022650018.jpg 2000w, https://www-img.bme.com/uploads/2025/04/005022650018-300x110.jpg 300w, https://www-img.bme.com/uploads/2025/04/005022650018-1024x374.jpg 1024w, https://www-img.bme.com/uploads/2025/04/005022650018-768x280.jpg 768w, https://www-img.bme.com/uploads/2025/04/005022650018-1536x561.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow">
