<div style="height:1rem" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center is-style-text-display has-x-large-font-size is-style-text-display--7">Wounds heal to become beautiful scars.</h2>



<p class="is-style-text-display has-large-font-size is-style-text-display--8" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:400">WELCOME BACK to the one and only Body Modification Ezine. It feels like a lifetime has passed, and for some of us, it has.</p>



<p class="is-style-text-display has-large-font-size is-style-text-display--9" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:400">We have inherited a remarkable and daunting legacy, and we ask for your continued support. Our goal is to both restore BME as much as we can, but also to build a new BME, one that will continue to evolve and grow beyond any one person’s vision.</p>



<p class="is-style-text-display has-large-font-size is-style-text-display--10" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:400">The world still needs a community dedicated to informed experimentation, responsible practice, and the unyielding spirit of those who choose to reshape themselves. Whether you are a seasoned veteran or a newcomer seeking guidance, BME exists to illuminate your path.</p>



<div class="wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-c936322e wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex" style="padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)">
<div class="wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-outline--11"><a class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://www.bme.com/about-us/">ABout US</a></div>



