<h2 class="wp-block-heading is-style-text-display is-style-text-display--14">Our Mission</h2>
</div>



<p class="is-style-default has-large-font-size"><strong>BME supports and celebrates the global body modification community.</strong> We provide a platform for individuals to share their experiences, art, and knowledge in a spirit of openness and respect. Our mission is to foster understanding, promote safety and education, and honor all forms of body modification without judgment. We strive to build community, encourage positive portrayals in mainstream culture, and protect the history and diversity of body art practices. In the face of challenges and change, we are committed to preserving BME’s spirit, archives, and traditions for future generations.</p>



<p class="is-style-default has-large-font-size">Through the contributions of our members, artists, and practitioners, BME remains a living testament to the power of self-expression and community. <strong>Together, we keep the legacy alive.</strong></p>



